  - Integrate real modules later by implementing the same contract.
[2026-03-02]
- Implemented standalone-first reusable flow engine in core to support client-custom module sequences before real modules exist.
- New core components:
  - FlowGraph: directed transition map with validation (validate_path, can_transition, next_options).
  - FlowEngine: executes fixed paths (run_path) and rule-driven paths (run_auto).
  - ModuleOutcome: standardized module output (context_updates, next_module, stop, reason).
  - Safety controls: max_steps and max_visits_per_module to permit repeats while preventing infinite loops.
- Integration contract:
